## State Management

Redux Toolkit.

Each feature owns:

- slice
- async thunks
- selectors
- types

---

## API Layer

All HTTP communication must be isolated inside:

features/*/api

Components must never call axios directly.

---

## Routing

Routes:

/
SearchPage

/settings
SettingsPage

---

## Layout

AppLayout

Contains:

- Top navigation bar
- Navigation links
- Main content area

---

## Data Flow

UI

↓

Dispatch thunk

↓

API service

↓

Backend

↓

Redux Store

↓

UI update

---

## Forbidden

- Business logic in components
- Direct API calls from components
- Global mutable state
- Context API for application state